Package: git4r
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Git For R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  person(given = "John",
         family = "Hobbs",
         role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "johnxhobbs@gmail.com")
Description: An interactive git user interface from the R command line. Intuitive
         tools to make commits, branches, remotes, and diffs an integrated part
         of R coding. Built on git2r, a sytem installation of git is not required
         and default on-premises-remote option avoids proxy issues.
